{"tid":1984410,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★失業綜援申請單月增10.9%　超越沙士時期水平","createTime":"2020-04-22T12:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T12:21:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c1ffc34718938e9e3b44ab2e30616d55794a6361","tid":1984410,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:19:37.000Z","msg":"社會福利署今日(22日)發表最新的領取綜合社會保障援助(綜援)個案數字，3月份整體領取綜援的個案較2月份增加2017宗，按月升幅為0.9%。其中因失業而領取綜援的個案數目達14,647宗，單月增幅達10.9%，超越2003年沙士時期水平。<br />\n<br />\n社署數字顯示，3月底領取綜援的個案總數為222,691宗，涉及人數共310,153。以個案分類，失業類別個案上升10.9%，有14,647宗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200422/bkn-20200422191438775-0422_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200422%2Fbkn-20200422191438775-0422_00822_001.html&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CkYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=f6ff0c65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200422/bkn-20200422191438775-0422_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"77d9c95e229e3bdecdb3d91f74a7ba58638c2c54","tid":1984410,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b1dd7df34abf2aabf688a7a5570be8a5599fdf","tid":1984410,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:21:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抽乾佢再走<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b5affa27b54a1ed04513c988f0638cb06eee2b96","tid":1984410,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:21:23.000Z","msg":"失